OL,5,G2305 24 Hours in A&E
OL,6,     FSunny is rushed to Queen's with
OL,7,     Fmultiple stab wounds. Tyler's hurt
OL,8,     Fhis foot playing football. And
OL,9,     Fdoctors are concerned about an
OL,10,     F87-year-old woman who's coughing
OL,11,     Fup blood.
OL,12,G0005 Emergency
